synopsis.text: Advantaged Talent) class, Tsugumi Harudori, a halberd-transforming student, finds herself in the 'NOT' (Normally Overcome Target) class at the Death Weapon Meister Academy (DWMA). Alongside her new friends, the airheaded Meme Tatane and the tsundere princess Anya Hepburn, Tsugumi navigates the challenges of controlling her powers and choosing a partner. Set one year before the events of Soul Eater, this spin-off story follows the everyday lives of these less talented students as they strive for normalcy amidst their unique abilities.
